snippet.title: Gunsheath (v0.2) - 7 Minutes of Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gunsheath is a hack-n-shmup (hack and slash and shoot-em-up!) game prototype where you take on the role of the skybound mech "Dyne" as they defend the world from an evil fleet of enemy ships.

Play it on Itch.io: https://nujakujata.itch.io/gunsheath
